data.description: Stately custom brick home nestled onto two lots in the highly desirable Beacon Hill subdivision. This home boasts an open concept, floor to ceiling windows, first floor primary w/ attached bath and custom closet. Perfect property for entertaining with a full finished walkout basement with wet bar and media area. Outdoor living area with saltwater pool and oversized detached garage. Rare opportunity in neighborhood with private unobstructed backyard views.
